Cell["\<\
of which one is very much larger than the others. We observe that some \
eigenvalues are real, some complex, and that the complex eigenvalues occur in \
conjugate pairs. Those reality/complixity/conjugacy distinctions are repeated \
when one looks to the corresponding eigenvectors:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.523479003459778*^9, 3.5234790789094276`*^9}, {
  3.523481572140039*^9, 3.52348159496432*^9}, {3.523481629073236*^9, 
